Uses of Package
org.jcvi.jillion.fasta

  • Packages that use org.jcvi.jillion.fasta 
    Package Description
    org.jcvi.jillion.fasta
    This package contains classes for dealing with fasta data.
    org.jcvi.jillion.fasta.aa
    This package deals with Fasta files that contain ProteinSequence data.
    org.jcvi.jillion.fasta.nt
    This package deals with Fasta files that contain NucleotideSequence data.
    org.jcvi.jillion.fasta.pos  
    org.jcvi.jillion.fasta.qual
    This package deals with Fasta files that contain QualitySequence data.
    org.jcvi.jillion.internal.fasta  
    org.jcvi.jillion.internal.fasta.aa  
    org.jcvi.jillion.internal.fasta.nt  
    org.jcvi.jillion.internal.fasta.qual  
    org.jcvi.jillion.maq.bfa
    This package supports reading and writing Maq's Binary Fasta File format .bfa.
    org.jcvi.jillion.shared.fasta
    Common classes that are used the different types of Fasta (nucleotide fasta, protein fasta etc) but aren't meant to be used by Jillion users.
  • Classes in org.jcvi.jillion.fasta used by org.jcvi.jillion.fasta 
    Class and Description
    FastaParser
    FastaParser is an interface that will parse a FASTA formatted structure and call the appropriate visit methods on the given FastaVisitor.
    FastaRecord
    FastaRecord is an interface for interacting with a single FASTA record.
    FastaRecordVisitor
    FastaRecordVisitor is a visitor interface to visit a single fasta record inside of a fasta file.
    FastaVisitor
    FastaVisitor is a visitor interface to visit components of a single fasta file.
    FastaVisitorCallback
    FastaVisitorCallback is a callback mechanism for the FastaVisitor instance to communicate with the parser that is parsing the fasta data.
    FastaVisitorCallback.FastaVisitorMemento
    FastaVisitorMemento is a marker interface that FastaParser instances can use to "rewind" back to the position in its fasta file in order to revisit portions of the fasta file.
    FastaWriter
    FastaWriter is a interface that handles how FastaRecords are written.
    FastaWriter.FastaRecordAdapter 
    SplitFastaWriter.DeconvolveFastaRecordWriterFactory
    Functional interface to create new FastaWriter instances.
    SplitFastaWriter.FastaRecordWriterFactory
    Functional interface to create new FastaWriter instances.
